Package: Gqr
Version: 0.2-0
Date: 2012-10-20
Title: Determine knots and weights for Gaussian quadrature rules
Author: Douglas Bates <bates@stat.wisc.edu>,
        Martin Maechler <maechler@R-project.org> and
	Ben Bolker <bolker@mcmaster.ca>
Maintainer: <lme4-authors@R-forge.wu-wien.ac.at>
Description: Determine the knots and the weights for Gaussian quadrature
 rules based on Legendre, Chebyshev, Gegenbauer, Jacobi, Laguerre,
 Hermite, Exponential or Rational kernels.  Generalized forms of the
 kernels can be used.
Depends: R(>= 2.14.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: sfsmisc
SuggestsNote: only for examples, etc
LazyLoad: yes
License: GPL (>=2)

